Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.03,0:24:56.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}どこかで呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.34,0:24:58.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}近づいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.10,0:25:01.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}真っ白な世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.12,0:25:06.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}たった一つだけの約束
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.92,0:25:18.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}きっと忘れないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.47,0:25:22.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}二人過ごした永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.33,0:25:25.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}照れ臭そうに手招く
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.83,0:25:29.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}無邪気な時の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:32.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}言葉で伝えるには
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.78,0:25:36.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}未完成な感情です
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.25,0:25:40.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}運命を嘆くほど
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.16,0:25:44.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}私たち弱くはない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.60,0:25:47.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}ねぇそうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:49.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}どこかで呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:51.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}動き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.68,0:25:54.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}選び取る答えに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:59.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}心ちぎれそうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:26:02.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}守りたいものがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.75,0:26:06.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}ためらいの朝　迷いの夜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.44,0:26:09.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}もし手を離しても
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.46,0:26:15.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}必ずたどり着くと信じてます
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.85,0:26:22.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}私を呼ぶ声が聞こえてる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.03,0:24:56.34,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在某处呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.34,0:24:58.10,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}离我近点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.10,0:25:01.12,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在纯白的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.12,0:25:06.51,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}只有一个承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.92,0:25:18.47,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我相信你不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.47,0:25:22.33,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我们一起度过的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.33,0:25:25.83,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}你的招呼让我害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.83,0:25:29.92,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在纯真的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:32.78,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}要我用言语说明
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.78,0:25:36.80,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}是一种不完整的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.25,0:25:40.16,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}命运的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.16,0:25:44.60,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我们的关系会更脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.60,0:25:47.39,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}嘿，对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:49.84,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在某处呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:51.68,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}快点来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.68,0:25:54.63,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我不知道怎么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:59.00,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}即使我放下我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:26:02.75,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}因为有想要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.75,0:26:06.44,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}早上的混乱，晚上的犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.44,0:26:09.46,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}就算放开你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.46,0:26:15.93,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我相信你会到达那里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.85,0:26:22.12,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}你能听见我的心声吗
